{"tid":878833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本要求中國撤除釣魚島周邊海域浮標","createTime":"2018-10-27T12:28:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T15:05:13.000Z","uid":39464,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"73af376164c9446e1b823820a86bbe947bbba998","tid":878833,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1425164_1_L_20181027162410.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1425164_1_L_20181027162410.jpg&h=9dbd52aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陪同日本首相安倍晉三訪華的外相河野太郎，昨日與中國國務委員兼外長王毅會談。共同社報道，河野要求中國撤除在尖閣諸島、即中國釣魚島周邊海域設置的浮標。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，王毅未有直接回應，但考慮到東海問題等，強調將妥善處理雙方的分歧。雙方同意決心使東海成為和平、合作、友好之海。日本外務省表示，浮標設在日本專屬經濟區之內。<br />\n<br />\n另外，河野及王毅又同意就中國放寬福島核事故後針對日本產食品的進口限制，繼續溝通。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1425164-20181027.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1425164-20181027.htm&d=BBMsXovDUggW2io7Z2ScBQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=815b5692\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1425164-20181027.htm&h=cffbffd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1425164-20181027.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c9ad0c290a1ed94df0ec9a41e48b8cc8a381fabb","tid":878833,"uid":35135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:50:34.000Z","msg":"中日友好,個島仔就豪俾佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e890c0617105f455a504a2200ea6cacd3f210e","tid":878833,"uid":215634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:14:57.000Z","msg":"同你扮friend，實情撳住黎搶"},{"pid":"8b32035e5948672a07220c028bfe143254f8573b","tid":878833,"uid":47259,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:16:18.000Z","msg":"趁你病攞你命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class